Title: Duality in 2D Spin Models on Torus
Author: A.I. Bugrij, V.N. Shadura
Comments: 10 pages, LATEX. Reference added
Report-no: ITEP-TH-20/97
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Statistical Mechanics
\\
  Method of derivation of the duality relations for two-dimensional
Z(N)-symmetric spin models on finite square lattice wrapped on the torus is
proposed. As example, exact duality relations for the nonhomogeneous Ising
model (N=2) and the Z(N)-Berezinsky-Villain model are obtained.
